  "title": "Social Media / Digital Marketing Executive (Training Provided) - Entry Levels are Welcome~!",
  "description": "<p><strong>Digital Marketing Executive (Retail/ F&B ) </strong><br />Working Days & hours: 5 days, Mon – Fri , 10am – 7pm<br />Location: Pasir Panjang<br />Salary: $2500 - $3000</p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and update social media platforms (Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, etc.)</li><li>Create content for luxury watch products and F&B promotions</li><li>Plan and execute digital marketing campaigns and seasonal promotion.</li><li>Coordinate with retail sales and F&B teams on marketing activities</li><li>Handle online enquiries and customer engagement</li><li>Track basic marketing performance and prepare simple reports</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>with 1 year of experience in digital marketing, preferably in retail, luxury, or F&B</li><li>Familiar with social media platforms (Instagram, Facebook, TikTok)</li><li>Basic content creation skills (Canva / simple video editing)</li></ul><p><strong>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619</strong><br /><strong>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
